## Recent Developments  

- **March 2025:** Oracle + NVIDIA – integration of NVIDIA inference software & GPUs with Oracle Cloud Infrastructure (OCI) for fast, scalable generative AI deployment (160+ AI tools, NIM micro‑services, no‑code blueprints).  
- **March 2025:** Anthropic PBC – upgraded developer platform for Claude AI assistant to support team collaboration and advanced reasoning, addressing version control and collaboration gaps.  
- **September 2024:** Oracle + Amazon Web Services – launch of Oracle Database AWS, enabling access to Oracle Autonomous Database & Exadata within AWS, with integrated AI/ML capabilities.  

